# Performance

## Server

- Fetch only needed columns; avoid `select('*')` on wide JSONB rows
- Parallelize independent Supabase queries with `Promise.all`
- Use `revalidatePath` / `revalidateTag` surgically — not global revalidation

## Client

- Dynamic import heavy libs (`pptxgenjs`, `recharts`) only in export/preview paths
- Virtualize long slide lists if > 50 slides
- Debounce autosave in slide editor (300–500ms)

## Images

- `next/image` for screenshots and brand logos
- Store originals in Supabase Storage; serve via signed URLs

## AI & jobs

- Never block HTTP response on OpenAI calls — use Inngest
- Stream outline generation to UI when possible (AI SDK streaming)

## Bundle

- Audit with `@next/bundle-analyzer` before adding large deps
- Tree-shake lucide icons (import individual icons, not barrel)

## Monitoring

- Sentry for errors; PostHog for Web Vitals and funnel metrics
- Track p95 for deck generation and export completion times
